egacy modernization story with Commander-4 platform leadership, evaluation, guardrails, and observability instead of letting the AdTech transformation dominate alone.","section":"summary","why_now":"Summary balance is currently the biggest representation gap between existing evidence and category fit.","supported_by":["data/master-cv/role_metadata.json:3","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:28","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:163","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:282","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:332"],"citation":"The current summary captures architecture delivery well but misses the strongest AI-quality-control evidence already in the record."},{"priority_rank":3,"action":"Reorder top Seven.One bullets so the current-role story reads as architecture + production AI quality + stakeholder influence, not architecture alone.","section":"role_bullets","why_now":"This category rewards a combined narrative of architecture, delivery, reliability, evaluation, governance, and translation.","supported_by":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:123","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:163","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:250","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:266","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:282","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:332"],"citation":"Several category-critical bullets already exist but are not prioritized together in the top narrative."},{"priority_rank":4,"action":"Regroup skills around platform architecture, observability, evaluation, guardrails, integration, and gateway design before lower-level tool names.","section":"skills","why_now":"The current skills layer is technically rich but can read tool-heavy rather than architecture-and-quality oriented.","supported_by":["data/master-cv/projects/commander4_skills.json:22","data/master-cv/projects/commander4_skills.json:36","data/